entry.title: At Least 150 Injured in Clashes at Jerusalem Holy Site
entry.content: Israeli police said young masked men used fireworks, stones and other heavy objects to attack security forces around Al Aqsa mosque.

entry.title: Kyiv Rocked by Explosions as Russia Steps Up Attacks
entry.content: Russia threatened to escalate attacks on Ukrainian command centers in response to alleged strikes inside Russian territory, with both sides gearing up for a new stage in the ground war.
